 qemu-kvm | qemu-system,
Suggests:
 libvirt-daemon-system (= ${source:Version}),
 numad,
Enhances:
 qemu-kvm,
 qemu-system,
 xen,
Breaks:
 libvirt-clients (<< 6.9.0-2~),
 libvirt-daemon-system (<< 6.9.0-3~),
Replaces:
 libvirt-daemon-system (<< 6.9.0-3~),

